    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Does it handle parts inventory and spare allocation?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Each technician has a virtual van stock. Parts consumed update the master inventory, trigger reorder when low, and flag warranty vs chargeable usage on the job card.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can customers track technician arrival like Uber?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Customers receive an SMS or WhatsApp link showing the technician name, photo, ETA, and live GPS location, just like ride-hailing apps. This reduces no-show calls and improves CSAT.</div>
